column2: SELECT s.plate,s.mjd,s.ra,s.dec,s.fiberid into MyDB.DESI_SDSS FROM galaxy AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect(#,#,#,#) AS b ON p.objID = b.objID UNION FROM galaxy AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid     JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect(#,#,#,#) AS b ON p.objID = b.objID WHERE  (s.specClass = dbo.fSpecClass(&&&)) AND s.z < # AND p.r < # AND (p.g - p.r) > #
